Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:15.29,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go take a walk in chains of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:21.36,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,I... to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:23.12,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...might love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}Sword of the {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Holy Man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.98,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}Sword of the {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Holy Man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:40.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:40.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Vallière Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmorency, I'm headed off to join the army now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to see me off with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you might die when you go off to war?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To die protecting one's country...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this not the most honourable death for an aristocrat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about honour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, we'll never see each other again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you... care that much about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmorency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the army really is going to march into Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They drafted all the boys in the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rough being an aristocrat, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all the boys were drafted,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that leaves me as the sole remaining young male in the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you imagining?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmorency?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't give me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Julio Chesaré.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a transfer student from Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the colour of a flame becomes fainter as its temperature rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are several metals that cannot be processed without a hot flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he's a flamen from Romalia, so he isn't joining the military
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why come to a magic academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares as long as he's handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the girls are looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the blondie that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better than a dog I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be popular that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you? Aren't you interested in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, out to the field, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness' Musketeer Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been stationed at this school in order to provide you with military drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class is cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are continuing the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, we are in the midst of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not a time to be holding classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is {\i1}because{\i0} we are in a war that we must learn how foolish it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the boys have joined the military,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I would like you to not bring war onto this campus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate mages...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,especially those who use fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate mages?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not interfere with my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're mages!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's practice practical magic, whether offensive or defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat me using magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do anything once you get your wand taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were an enemy, you would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what might happen in a real battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with a wand in your hand, you may not have enough time to cast your spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the very basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skills with which to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:06:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about a private lesson with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, but my partner has already been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who's your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, may I call you Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, why Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That snobby son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so close to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not a student at this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemy were to come right now, would you not be fighting as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only use practical weapons well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can also defeat an enemy with a wooden sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Give me a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boring fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing to my familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him fight the other day, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...his level was beyond mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he was holding Delflinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delflinger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a real sword or a practical weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use my skill as a familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so your skill wasn't sharpened as a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you to fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use your Delf... whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to fight against you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am merely curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the winner of the fight gets to kiss Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, kiss? Stop making stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a flamen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told, in order to come to Tristain, I have temporarily returned to secular life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I am allowed to wield a sword as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off! Don't touch Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a flamen or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so snobby it bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to fight or whatever, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting all worked up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get serious, he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're worried about him and not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now isn't the time to be creating trivial problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on fighting, use the wooden sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to use a real sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight tomorrow morning using wooden swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, calling me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a ridiculous request...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Teach me how to fight with swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've... never seriously learnt swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a real weapon, I can use it the moment it's in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I hold a sword, my body moves on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the power of Gandalfr, the legendary familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandalfr?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that I should rely solely on that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were suddenly attacked like how the vice-captain did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and caught without a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that'd be the end of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this war... there could be lots of danger ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I can't protect Louise unless I become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you want me to teach you swordsmanship for the sake of protecting Miss Vallière?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I want to win tomorrow's fight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't bring myself to like that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like flashy guys, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Saito, can you keep up with my training?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me! He isn't in our room, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where did you hide him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not hiding him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand! There is no time to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you have the form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By experiencing real battle, you must have picked up the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But form alone will not help you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike at the opponent's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Saito, I saw him in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with the captain of the Musketeer Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Captain, do you mean Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were breathing hard and drenched in sweat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike at the opening, she says...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, where do I even find an opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you said that you don't like mages who use fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got something against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. That's the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.27,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dirty dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look as though you were beaten all night long by a dragon in a jealous rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... that's actually what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind calling off the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get started, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, is that kiss ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're rooting for Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because whoever wins gets to kiss Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You can't bear to see Julio-sama kiss Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my partner's doing pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can he win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, he'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent's too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a flamen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to kiss Louise that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you returned to secular life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but didn't you really get kicked out for being a womaniser?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A plan to aggravate me, then striking during the opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amateur trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun, not only do I want to kiss Louise,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kiss you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Julio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it. Are you hurt at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more than the wounds you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of response was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, my partner wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chance to do so with permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want... to.. kiss me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you beat Julio, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lost on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With partner's current skill, there was no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fooling around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, you didn't have to refuse me in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looked as if I... I was rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Code name Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job. Step outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What was the meaning of that battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am interested in neither win nor loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to know the strength of my team-mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team-mate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is your team-mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise. Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for my familiar's rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you two, I was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure he was, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard what happened to Prince Wales as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Albion's conspiracy after all, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I am your team-mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romalia's pope senses danger from Albion as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he sent me to lend my hand to the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both he and I wish to avoid the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the situation is profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, Saito-san, Julio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are those upon whom I rely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:20:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in other words, you concentrated your force to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You have something to say about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just bothered by what Colbert-sensei said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "don't bring war onto the campus" thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of subjecting the school to the dangers of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly want to borrow your strength for the sake of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we'll get along well, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stay away from Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! What are you blushing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bright, bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're a dog, and you dare make fun of your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I must start with an unfortunate piece of news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tristain's Queen, Henrietta, on her day of coronation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has executed our King, Lord Cromwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, in thirst for more blood, Henrietta is increasing her military forces in order to invade our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheffield... She was Lord Cromwell's secretary...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now she's acting like the new King rather than a magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:37.60,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It is now time to show the true power of Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:42.68,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall repel all the enemies that come,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, when she stands before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot object against her authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:46.24,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,and execute the detestable Henrietta with our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magistrate Sheffield!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do anything to Eléonore-oneesama or Cattleya-neesama, you won't stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vallière Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
